  "description": "Something enormous breathes once every twenty seconds at 3,000 meters. Each breath lights the water column in a flash of blue-white. This is not a fish. Science has no name for this. The bioRate is 0.05 Hz — a single breath per twenty seconds. The bioBrightness peaks at 1800 Hz — alien spectral territory.",
